### 7. End-to-End Sandbox Workflow Test
- Test complete sandbox lifecycle from creation to deletion:
  ```typescript
  it('should handle complete sandbox lifecycle', async () => {
    // Create sandbox
    const sandbox = await sandboxManager.createSandbox('e2e-portfolio', {});
    expect(sandbox.state).toBe(SandboxState.CREATING);

    // Build and run
    await sandboxManager.buildSandbox(sandbox.id);
    await sandboxManager.runSandbox(sandbox.id);

    // Generate preview URL
    const previewUrl = await previewManager.generatePreviewUrl(sandbox.id);
    expect(previewUrl).toBeDefined();

    // Verify preview is accessible
    const response = await fetch(previewUrl);
    expect(response.status).toBe(200);

    // Stop and archive
    await sandboxManager.stopSandbox(sandbox.id);
    await sandboxManager.archiveSandbox(sandbox.id);

    // Verify final state
    const finalSandbox = await sandboxManager.getSandbox(sandbox.id);
    expect(finalSandbox.state).toBe(SandboxState.ARCHIVED);
  });
  ```

